Why Lambdas?
---------------
--> Enables functional programming : In addition to writing object oriented programs in Java, Lambdas enable us to write functional programs in Java
--> Readable and Concise code : Lambdas eliminate some of the boilerplate code that you'll have to write.
--> Easier-to-use APIs and libraries : Helps us to write better APIs and libraries which are easier to use.
--> Enables support for parallel processing : Having suppport for parallel processing helps us to write better code that runs on multi-core processors. 
